content:
The Insurance Property & Casualty Application provides examples of insurance applications for various lines of business, including Auto, Watercraft, Homeowners, Business Owners, and Commercial. The application includes business processes, portals, and realistic product models to create quotes, issue policies, manage claims, and track commissions.

Lines of Business:

* Auto
* Watercraft
* Homeowners
* Business Owners
* Commercial

Business Processes:

Each line of business includes detailed business processes, which have been updated to allow for seamless transition from the Asset object model or Vlocity Insurance FSC extension object model to the Insurance Policy core object model.

User Personas:

* Broker/Agent: Larry Sullivan (uses Vlocity Broker Portal)
* End Customer: Ernie Newton (uses Vlocity Customer Portal)
* Internal Service Rep/Underwriter: Kevin Under (uses Vlocity Insurance Console, Vlocity Policy Administration)
* Claims Adjuster: Ed Brown (uses Vlocity Claims)
* Vlocity Admin: uses all applications

Applications:

* Vlocity Insurance
* Vlocity Service Console
* Vlocity Adjuster Dashboard
* Vlocity Administration

Portals:

* Digital Broker Self-Service Portal
* Digital Policyholder Self-Service Portal

The Most Important Objects:

* Product
* Quote
* Policies (Asset object)
* Claim

What's Next?

* Get a spin of the Property & Casualty Application org
* Choose a line of business to explore
* Learn about product models, rating procedures, and business processes
title: Insurance Property & Casualty Application Overview
